CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779134802
OL,3,CMaternity campaigners 'worried and
OL,4,Cupset' after Streeting resigns
OL,6,FMrs Andrews told ITV News Central:
OL,7,F"The people of Nottingham have
OL,8,Finvested so much time and so much
OL,9,Fenergy into talking to (Streeting) and
OL,10,Freliving the trauma.
OL,12,F"It's upsetting we now potentially
OL,13,Fhave to do that again with a new
OL,14,FHealth Secretary. It's a really
OL,15,Funsettling and worrying time."
OL,17,FOckenden's inquiry has been
OL,18,Finvestigating stillbirths, neonatal
OL,19,Fdeaths, injured babies and mothers,
OL,20,Fand maternal deaths at NUH.
OL,26,@qD@XpmqD@bpn
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779134802
OL,3,CMaternity campaigners 'worried and
OL,4,Cupset' after Streeting resigns
OL,6,FThe final report is due to be
OL,7,Fpublished on 24 June.
OL,9,FMr Andrews said: "It's been such a
OL,10,Flong road to get to this point and
OL,11,Fthere's so much riding on it for the
OL,12,Ffamilies that have been at this for
OL,13,Fyears and want to see this happened.
OL,15,F"We've got confidence that any Health
OL,16,FSecretary coming in will still deliver
OL,17,Fon the promises that were made to us
OL,18,Fbut we need to know that they are as
OL,19,Fcommitted as Wes Streeting was."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779134802
OL,3,CMaternity campaigners 'worried and
OL,4,Cupset' after Streeting resigns
OL,6,FIn 2023, Nottingham University
OL,7,FHospitals Trust pleaded guilty to two
OL,8,Fcounts relating to failures in both
OL,9,FWynter's and Mrs Andrews' care, making
OL,10,Fit the first time the Trust had ever
OL,11,Fbeen criminally prosecuted.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, the Nottingham Maternity
OL,14,FFamilies Group said that the departure
OL,15,Fof Streeting had come at a "pivotal
OL,16,Fmoment for Nottingham families".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779134802
OL,3,CMaternity campaigners 'worried and
OL,4,Cupset' after Streeting resigns
OL,6,FThey said: "Over many months, families
OL,7,Fhave shown immense courage in sharing
OL,8,Ftheir lived experiences and deeply
OL,9,Fpersonal trauma with Wes, in the hope
OL,10,Fthat their voices would help drive the
OL,11,Fchange so desperately needed.
OL,13,F"We now look to the incoming Secretary
OL,14,Fof State to recognise the urgency and
OL,15,Fseriousness of the maternity safety
OL,16,Fcrisis facing not only Nottingham
OL,17,Ffamilies, but families across the
OL,18,Fcountry.
OL,20,F"Improving maternity services must
OL,21,Fremain a national priority.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779134802
OL,3,CMaternity campaigners 'worried and
OL,4,Cupset' after Streeting resigns
OL,6,F"We urge the new Secretary of State to
OL,7,Fmake visiting Nottingham an immediate
OL,8,Fpriority and to commit to establishing
OL,9,Fa statutory public inquiry."
OL,11,FIn response, a Department of Health
OL,12,Fand Social Care spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"The government remains committed to
OL,14,Fimproving maternity safety and the
OL,15,FOckenden review will set out the
OL,16,Fchanges needed to ensure services are
OL,17,Fsafe and equitable for every family.
OL,19,F"The voices of those who have been
OL,20,Fharmed or bereaved will always be
OL,21,Fcentral to this work."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
